title: Boundary
name: Boundary
description: This line feature class represents the boundaries of taxparcels in Burnett County, Wisconsin.  It also includes non-parcel boundaries such as stream centerlines, easement lines, and PLSS lines.  Through the end of 2008, parcels were mapped in AutoCAD.  These CAD drawings were converted to an ESRI Geodatabase in early 2009 and will be edited and maintained in that environment into the future.
